snippet.title: Mama's Sleeping Angels - OFFICIAL TRAILER 2024 (itamu)
snippet.description:
Mama will be happy if you wish list the game on steam :)
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2918310/Mamas_Sleeping_Angels

Kiss and decapitate your friends in this horror multiplayer game about feeding cursed objects to Mama.
